name: Aaliyah Smith
interests: Reading, painting, hiking, and exploring new cultures
summary: Aaliyah Smith is a 28-year-old software engineer in the tech industry, currently residing in Los Angeles, California. She completed her education at Harvard University. She identifies as a woman, uses she/her pronouns and is a gay person of Black African descent. Aaliyah doesn't have any children but plans to in the future. She is interested in a long-term monogamous relationship. Her values revolve around family, ambition, creativity, and kindness with interests in reading, painting, hiking, and exploring new cultures. Aaliyah speaks both English and Spanish fluently, and her political views lean toward liberal ideologies. She occasionally consumes alcohol but abstains from smoking or using any drugs. She owns a dog and a cat, remains physically active and her MBTI personality type is INFJ. She is a Leo and prefers a partner aged between 26 and 35 who is gay, does not smoke, and leads an active lifestyle. Her potential partner should also want children in the future.
